 5   LESSON 31.
 6   
 7   I am not the victim of the world I see.
 8   W-pI.31.1. Today's idea is the introduction to your declaration of release. 2 Again, 
 9   the idea should be applied to both the world you see without and the world you see within.
10   3 In applying the idea, we will use a form of practice which will be used more and more,
11    with changes as indicated. 4 Generally speaking, the form includes two aspects, one in
12   which you apply the idea on a more sustained basis, and the other consisting of 
13   frequent applications of the idea throughout the day.
14   W-pI.31.2. Two longer periods of practice with the idea for today are needed, one in 
15   the morning and one at night. 2 Three to five minutes for each of these are recommended. 3
16   During that time, look about you slowly while repeating the idea two or three times. 4 
17   Then close your eyes, and apply the same idea to your inner world. 5 You will escape from 
18   both together, for the inner is the cause of the outer.
19   W-pI.31.3. As you survey your inner world, merely let whatever thoughts cross your mind
20   come into your awareness, each to be considered for a moment, and then replaced by the 
21   next. 2 Try not to establish any kind of hierarchy among them. 3 Watch them come and go as 
22   dispassionately as possible. 4 Do not dwell on any one in particular, but try to let the stream move 
23   on evenly and calmly, without any special investment on your part. 5 As you sit and 
24   quietly watch your thoughts, repeat today's idea to yourself as often as you care to, but with
25   no sense of hurry.
26   W-pI.31.4. In addition, repeat the idea for today as often as possible during the day. 
27   2 Remind yourself that you are making a declaration of independence in the name of your 
28   own freedom. 3 And in your freedom lies the freedom of the world.
29   W-pI.31.5. The idea for today is also a particularly useful one to use as a response to
30   any form of temptation that may arise. 2 It is a declaration that you will not yield to
31   it, and put yourself in bondage.
