39   These ideas are for review today:
40   W-pI.58.1. (36) My holiness envelops everything I see. 
41   2 From my holiness does the perception of the real world come. 3 Having forgiven, I no 
42   longer see myself as guilty. 4 I can accept the innocence that is the truth about me. 5 Seen 
43   through understanding eyes, the holiness of the world is all I see, for I can picture only the
44   thoughts I hold about myself.
45   
46   W-pI.58.2. (37) My holiness blesses the world. 
