38   LESSON 62.
39   
40   Forgiveness is my function as the light of the world.
41   W-pI.62.1. It is your forgiveness that will bring the world of darkness to the light. 2
42   It is your forgiveness that lets you recognize the light in which you see. 3 
43   Forgiveness is the demonstration that you are the light of the world. 4 Through your forgiveness 
44   does the truth about yourself return to your memory. 5 Therefore, in your forgiveness lies 
45   your salvation.
46   W-pI.62.2. Illusions about yourself and the world are one. 2 That is why all 
47   forgiveness is a gift to yourself. 3 Your goal is to find out who you are, having denied your 
48   Identity by attacking creation and its Creator. 4 Now you are learning how to remember the 
49   truth. 5 For this attack must be replaced by forgiveness, so that thoughts of life may 
50   replace thoughts of death.
0457
 1   W-pI.62.3. Remember that in every attack you call upon your own weakness, while each 
 2   time you forgive you call upon the strength of Christ in you. 2 Do you not then begin to 
 3   understand what forgiveness will do for you? 3 It will remove all sense of weakness, strain and 
 4   fatigue from your mind. 4 It will take away all fear and guilt and pain. 5 It will restore the
 5   invulnerability and power God gave His Son to your awareness.
 6   W-pI.62.4. Let us be glad to begin and end this day by practicing today's idea, and to 
 7   use it as frequently as possible throughout the day. 2 It will help to make the day as 
 8   happy for you as God wants you to be. 3 And it will help those around you, as well as those 
 9   who seem to be far away in space and time, to share this happiness with you.
10   W-pI.62.5. As often as you can, closing your eyes if possible, say to yourself today: 
11   
12   2 Forgiveness is my function as the light of the world. 3 I would fulfill my function 
13   that I may be happy. 
14   
15   4 Then devote a minute or two to considering your function and the happiness and 
16   release it will bring you. 5 Let related thoughts come freely, for your heart will recognize 
17   these words, and in your mind is the awareness they are true. 6 Should your attention wander,
18    repeat the idea and add: 
19   
20   7 I would remember this because I want to be happy.
