41   LESSON 81.
42   
43   Our ideas for review today are:
44   W-pI.81.1. (61) I am the light of the world.
45   2 How holy am I, who have been given the function of lighting up the world! 3 Let me be
46   still before my holiness. 4 In its calm light let all my conflicts disappear. 5 In its 
47   peace let me remember Who I am.
48   W-pI.81.2. Some specific forms for applying this idea when special difficulties seem to
49   arise might be: 
50   
0480
 1   2 Let me not obscure the light of the world in me. 
 2   3 Let the light of the world shine through this appearance. 
 3   4 This shadow will vanish before the light.
 4   
 5   W-pI.81.3. (62) Forgiveness is my function as the light of the world. 
 6   2 It is through accepting my function that I will see the light in me. 3 And in this 
 7   light will my function stand clear and perfectly unambiguous before my sight. 4 My 
 8   acceptance does not depend on my recognizing what my function is, for I do not yet understand 
 9   forgiveness. 5 Yet I will trust that, in the light, I will see it as it is.
10   W-pI.81.4. Specific forms for using this idea might include: 
11   
12   2 Let this help me learn what forgiveness means. 
13   3 Let me not separate my function from my will. 
14   4 I will not use this for an alien purpose.
