20   We will review these ideas today:
21   W-pI.82.1. (63) The light of the world brings peace to every mind through my 
22   forgiveness.
23   2 My forgiveness is the means by which the light of the world finds expression through 
24   me. 3 My forgiveness is the means by which I become aware of the light of the world in me.
25    4 My forgiveness is the means by which the world is healed, together with myself. 5 
26   Let me, then, forgive the world, that it may be healed along with me.
27   W-pI.82.2. Suggestions for specific forms for applying this idea are: 
28   
