34   2 I would not forget my function, because I would remember my Self. 3 I cannot fulfill 
35   my function if I forget it. 4 And unless I fulfill my function, I will not experience the
36   joy that God intends for me.
37   W-pI.82.4. Suitable specific forms of this idea include: 
38   
39   2 Let me not use this to hide my function from me. 
40   3 I would use this as an opportunity to fulfill my function. 
41   4 This may threaten my ego, but cannot change my function in any way.
