28   cannot die. 4 I am not a body. 5 I would recognize my reality today. 6 I will worship 
29   no idols, nor raise my own self-concept to replace my Self. 7 I am in the likeness of my 
30   Creator. 8 Love created me like itself.
31   W-pI.84.2. You might find these specific forms helpful in applying the idea: 
