40   obscure. 4 If I hold grievances I am attacking love, and therefore attacking my Self. 5 My 
41   Self thus becomes alien to me. 6 I am determined not to attack my Self today, so that I can
42   remember Who I am.
43   W-pI.84.4. These specific forms for applying this idea would be helpful: 
44   
