33   These ideas are for review today:
34   W-pI.86.1. (71) Only God's plan for salvation will work. 
35   2 It is senseless for me to search wildly about for salvation. 3 I have seen it in many
36   people and in many things, but when I reached for it, it was not there. 4 I was 
37   mistaken about where it is. 5 I was mistaken about what it is. 6 I will undertake no more idle 
38   seeking. 7 Only God's plan for salvation will work. 8 And I will rejoice because His plan can 
39   never fail.
40   W-pI.86.2. These are some suggested forms for applying this idea specifically: 
