13   comes first, and time must elapse before it can be worked out. 4 I do not see the 
14   problem and the answer as simultaneous in their occurrence. 5 That is because I do not yet 
15   realize that God has placed the answer together with the problem, so that they cannot be 
16   separated by time. 6 The Holy Spirit will teach me this, if I will let Him. 7 And I will 
