 4   for His assurance every time you speak the words He offers you today, and let Him tell 
 5   your mind that they are true. 4 Use them against temptation, and escape its sorry 
 6   consequences if you yield to the belief that you are something else. 5 The Holy Spirit gives you 
 7   peace today. 6 Receive His words, and offer them to Him.
