28   LESSON 99.
29   
30   Salvation is my only function here.
31   W-pI.99.1. Salvation and forgiveness are the same. 2 They both imply that something has
32   gone wrong; something to be saved from, forgiven for; something amiss that needs 
33   corrective change; something apart or different from the Will of God. 3 Thus do both terms imply 
34   a thing impossible but yet which has occurred, resulting in a state of conflict seen 
35   between what is and what could never be.
36   W-pI.99.2. Truth and illusions both are equal now, for both have happened. 2 The 
37   impossible becomes the thing you need forgiveness for, salvation from. 3 Salvation now becomes 
38   the borderland between the truth and the illusion. 4 It reflects the truth because it is 
39   the means by which you can escape illusions. 5 Yet it is not yet the truth because it 
40   undoes what was never done.
41   W-pI.99.3. How could there be a meeting place at all where earth and Heaven can be 
42   reconciled within a mind where both of them exist? 2 The mind that sees illusions thinks them 
43   real. 3 They have existence in that they are thoughts. 4 And yet they are not real, because
44   the mind that thinks these thoughts is separate from God.
45   W-pI.99.4. What joins the separated mind and thoughts with Mind and Thought which are 
46   forever One? 2 What plan could hold the truth inviolate, yet recognize the need illusions 
47   bring, and offer means by which they are undone without attack and with no touch of pain? 3 
48   What but a Thought of God could be this plan, by which the never done is overlooked, and 
49   sins forgotten which were never real?
50   W-pI.99.5. The Holy Spirit holds this plan of God exactly as it was received of Him 
0497
 1   within the Mind of God and in your own. 2 It is apart from time in that its Source is 
 2   timeless. 3 Yet it operates in time, because of your belief that time is real. 4 Unshaken does 
 3   the Holy Spirit look on what you see; on sin and pain and death, on grief and separation 
 4   and on loss. 5 Yet does He know one thing must still be true; God is still Love, and this 
 5   is not His Will.
 6   W-pI.99.6. This is the Thought that brings illusions to the truth, and sees them as 
 7   appearances behind which is the changeless and the sure. 2 This is the Thought that saves and that
 8   forgives, because it lays no faith in what is not created by the only Source it knows. 
 9   3 This is the Thought whose function is to save by giving you its function as your own. 
10   4 Salvation is your function, with the One to Whom the plan was given. 5 Now are you 
11   entrusted with this plan, along with Him. 6 He has one answer to appearances; regardless of 
12   their form, their size, their depth or any attribute they seem to have: 
13   
14   7 Salvation is my only function here.
15   8 God still is Love, and this is not His Will.
16   
17   W-pI.99.7. You who will yet work miracles, be sure you practice well the idea for today.
18    2 Try to perceive the strength in what you say, for these are words in which your 
19   freedom lies. 3 Your Father loves you. 4 All the world of pain is not His Will. 5 Forgive 
20   yourself the thought He wanted this for you. 6 Then let the Thought with which He has replaced 
21   all your mistakes enter the darkened places of your mind that thought the thoughts that 
22   never were His Will.
23   W-pI.99.8. This part belongs to God, as does the rest. 2 It does not think its solitary
24   thoughts, and make them real by hiding them from Him. 3 Let in the light, and you will 
25   look upon no obstacle to what He wills for you. 4 Open your secrets to His kindly light, 
26   and see how bright this light still shines in you.
27   W-pI.99.9. Practice His Thought today, and let His light seek out and lighten up all 
28   darkened spots, and shine through them to join them to the rest. 2 It is God's Will your mind 
29   be one with His. 3 It is God's Will that He has but one Son. 4 It is God's Will that His 
30   one Son is you. 5 Think of these things in practicing today, and start the lesson that we 
31   learn today with this instruction in the way of truth: 
