39   and peace. 2 You cannot lose the gifts your Father gave. 3 You do not want to be 
40   another self. 4 You have no function that is not of God. 5 Forgive yourself the one you think 
41   you made. 6 Forgiveness and salvation are the same. 7 Forgive what you have made and you 
42   are saved.
