19   I share God's Will for happiness for me.
20   W-pI.102.1. You do not want to suffer. 2 You may think it buys you something, and may 
21   still believe a little that it buys you what you want. 3 Yet this belief is surely shaken 
22   now, at least enough to let you question it, and to suspect it really makes no sense. 4 It
23   has not gone as yet, but lacks the roots that once secured it tightly to the dark and 
24   hidden secret places of your mind.
25   W-pI.102.2. Today we try to loose its weakened hold still further, and to realize that 
26   pain is purposeless, without a cause and with no power to accomplish anything. 2 It cannot 
27   purchase anything at all. 3 It offers nothing, and does not exist. 4 And everything you think 
28   it offers you is lacking in existence, like itself. 5 You have been slave to nothing. 6 
29   Be you free today to join the happy Will of God.
30   W-pI.102.3. For several days we will continue to devote our periods of practicing to 
31   exercises planned to help you reach the happiness God's Will has placed in you. 2 Here is your 
32   home, and here your safety is. 3 Here is your peace, and here there is no fear. 4 Here is 
33   salvation. 5 Here is rest at last.
34   W-pI.102.4. Begin your practice periods today with this acceptance of God's Will for 
35   you: 
