40   choice. 4 You cannot fail to find it when you learn it is your choice, and that you share 
41   God's Will.
42   W-pI.102.5. Be happy, for your only function here is happiness. 2 You have no need to 
43   be less loving to God's Son than He Whose Love created him as loving as Himself. 3 
44   Besides these hourly five-minute rests, pause frequently today, to tell yourself that you have
45   now accepted happiness as your one function. 4 And be sure that you are joining with 
46   God's Will in doing this.
