0624
 1   Let us instead be thankful for the gifts our Father gave us. 3 Can we see in those with 
 2   whom He shares His glory any trace of sin and guilt? 4 And can it be that we are not among 
 3   them, when He loves His Son forever and with perfect constancy, knowing he is as He created
 4   him?
