 7   
 8   This holy instant is salvation come.
 9   W-pII.241.1. What joy there is today! 2 It is a time of special celebration. 3 For 
10   today holds out the instant to the darkened world where its release is set. 4 The day has 
11   come when sorrows pass away and pain is gone. 5 The glory of salvation dawns today upon a 
12   world set free. 6 This is the time of hope for countless millions. 7 They will be united now,
13    as you forgive them all. 8 For I will be forgiven by you today.
14   
15   W-pII.241.2.  <We have forgiven one another now, and so we come at last to You again. 2
16   Father, Your Son, who never left, returns to Heaven and his home. 3 How glad are we to 
17   have our sanity restored to us, and to remember that we all are one.>
