39   Today I will judge nothing that occurs.
40   W-pII.243.1. I will be honest with myself today. 2 I will not think that I already know
41   what must remain beyond my present grasp. 3 I will not think I understand the whole 
42   from bits of my perception, which are all that I can see. 4 Today I recognize that this is 
43   so. 5 And so I am relieved of judgments that I cannot make. 6 Thus do I free myself and 
44   what I look upon, to be in peace as God created us.
45   
