30   Forgiveness ends all suffering and loss.
31   W-pII.249.1. Forgiveness paints a picture of a world where suffering is over, loss 
32   becomes impossible and anger makes no sense. 2 Attack is gone, and madness has an end. 3 What 
33   suffering is now conceivable? 4 What loss can be sustained? 5 The world becomes a place of joy, 
34   abundance, charity and endless giving. 6 It is now so like to Heaven that it quickly is 
35   transformed into the light that it reflects. 7 And so the journey which the Son of God began has 
36   ended in the light from which he came.
