 3   Love gave life to it. 2 And would I look upon what You created as if it could be made 
 4   sinful? 3 I would not perceive such dark and fearful images. 4 A madman's dream is hardly fit
 5   to be my choice, instead of all the loveliness with which You blessed creation; all its
 6   purity, its joy, and its eternal, quiet home in You.>
 7   
