17   and my Source, created me. 3 This the determination not to be asleep in dreams of death, 
18   while truth remains forever living in the joy of love. 4 And this the choice to recognize 
19   the Self Whom God created as the Son He loves, and Who remains my one Identity.
20   
21   W-pII.282.2.  <Father, Your Name is Love and so is mine. 2 Such is the truth. 3 And can
22   the truth be changed by merely giving it another name? 4 The name of fear is simply a 
23   mistake. 5 Let me not be afraid of truth today.>
