29   My true Identity abides in You.
30   W-pII.283.1.  <Father, I made an image of myself, and it is this I call the Son of God.
31   2 Yet is creation as it always was, for Your creation is unchangeable. 3 Let me not 
32   worship idols. 4 I am he my Father loves. 5 My holiness remains the light of Heaven and the 
33   Love of God. 6 Is not what is beloved of You secure? 7 Is not the light of Heaven infinite?
34   8 Is not Your Son my true Identity, when You created everything that is?>
35   
