43   You are my goal, my Father. Only You.
44   W-pII.287.1. Where would I go but Heaven? 2 What could be a substitute for happiness? 3
45   What gift could I prefer before the peace of God? 4 What treasure would I seek and find
46   and keep that can compare with my Identity? 5 And would I rather live with fear than 
47   love?
