50   What way but that which leads to You could I desire to walk? 4 And what except the memory 
0642
 1   of You could signify to me the end of dreams and futile substitutions for the truth? 5 
 2   You are my only goal. 6 Your Son would be as You created him. 7 What way but this could I 
 3   expect to recognize my Self, and be at one with my Identity?>
