0643
 1   W-pII.290.2.  <With this resolve I come to You, and ask Your strength to hold me up 
 2   today, while I but seek to do Your Will. 2 You cannot fail to hear me, Father. 3 What I ask 
 3   have You already given me. 4 And I am sure that I will see my happiness today.>
