 4   A happy outcome to all things is sure.
 5   W-pII.292.1. God's promises make no exceptions. 2 And He guarantees that only joy can 
 6   be the final outcome found for everything. 3 Yet it is up to us when this is reached; how
 7   long we let an alien will appear to be opposing His. 4 And while we think this will is 
 8   real, we will not find the end He has appointed as the outcome of all problems we perceive,
 9   all trials we see, and every situation that we meet. 5 Yet is the ending certain. 6 For
10   God's Will is done in earth and Heaven. 7 We will seek and we will find according to 
11   His Will, which guarantees that our will is done.
12   
