24   Can the world seem bright and clear and safe and welcoming, with all my past mistakes 
25   oppressing it, and showing me distorted forms of fear? 4 Yet in the present love is obvious, and 
26   its effects apparent. 5 All the world shines in reflection of its holy light, and I 
