30   am abandoned or unneeded in the world. 3 This is my home because I judge it not, and 
31   therefore is it only what You will. 4 Let me today behold it uncondemned, through happy eyes 
32   forgiveness has released from all distortion. 5 Let me see Your world instead of mine. 6 And all 
33   the tears I shed will be forgotten, for their source is gone. 7 Father, I will not judge 
34   Your world today.>
