0668
 1   And certainty of purpose. And in Him 
 2   Is His Creator, as He is in me.
 3   W-pII.354.1.  <My oneness with the Christ establishes me as Your Son, beyond the reach 
 4   of time, and wholly free of every law but Yours. 2 I have no self except the Christ in me.
 5    3 I have no purpose but His Own. 4 And He is like His Father. 5 Thus must I be one 
 6   with You as well as Him. 6 For who is Christ except Your Son as You created Him? 7 And what
 7   am I except the Christ in me?>
