12   
13   There is no end to all the peace and joy, 
14   And all the miracles that I will give, 
15   When I accept God's Word. Why not today?
16   W-pII.355.1.  <Why should I wait, my Father, for the joy You promised me? 2 For You 
17   will keep Your Word You gave Your Son in exile. 3 I am sure my treasure waits for me, and I
18   need but reach out my hand to find it. 4 Even now my fingers touch it. 5 It is very 
19   close. 6 I need not wait an instant more to be at peace forever. 7 It is You I choose, and 
20   my Identity along with You. 8 Your Son would be Himself, and know You as his Father and 
21   Creator, and his Love.>
