25   LESSON 356.
26   
27   Sickness is but another name for sin. 
28   Healing is but another name for God. 
29   The miracle is thus a call to Him.
30   W-pII.356.1.  <Father, You promised You would never fail to answer any call Your Son 
31   might make to You. 2 It does not matter where he is, what seems to be his problem, nor what 
32   he believes he has become. 3 He is Your Son, and You will answer him. 4 The miracle 
33   reflects Your Love, and thus it answers him. 5 Your Name replaces every thought of sin, and who
34   is sinless cannot suffer pain. 6 Your Name gives answer to Your Son, because to call 
35   Your Name is but to call his own.>
36   
